summary: Adds various pines and ferns to Whiterun, making the town come to life with some greener foliage.
descriptionHtml:
Adds various pines and ferns to Whiterun, making the town come to life with some greener foliage.
I\'ll be adding to this mod over time as I find new foliage to add as i see fit :)

Note: My screens were captured with the Cinematic ENB mod on, I\'m too lazy to take it off to show vanilla :P

Update 1.1:

- Foliage now visible from outside the city walls. I\'ll tweak it as I look around and see any faults or possible improvements

1.2:
- Aspen trees added for fall color and variety
author: Valkyrie
